---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonials & Reviews for Tutors — SocialProof" description="Parents trust other parents. Collect testimonials from tutoring families and display them on your tutoring website — free for one widget." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/tutors">
<style>
    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .why-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .why-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .why-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .own-your-reviews { background: #f0fdf4; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .own-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .own-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .own-inner p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .quote-section blockquote { font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section cite { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: #111; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    nav { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; text-decoration: none; color: #111; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .btn-nav { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff !important; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
    footer a { color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px; }
    .steps-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .steps-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-content h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .faq-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .faq-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .faq-item { margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .faq-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
</style>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/for">Industries</a>
      <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-nav">Try free</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Testimonials for Tutors — Because Parents Trust Other Parents</h1>
  <p>When a parent is searching for a tutor, what they really want is proof it worked for someone else's child. Give them that proof on your website before they even reach out.</p>
  <div class="cta-group">
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
    <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why-section">
  <h2>Why testimonials win new tutoring clients</h2>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>Academic results are hard to show — testimonials make them real</h3>
      <p>You can't publish your students' grades. But when a parent writes "My son went from failing algebra to a B+ in one semester," that's powerful. Specific outcome testimonials do what credentials alone can't.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>Tutoring Craigslist pages have no personality</h3>
      <p>Most tutors are listed on generic platforms with no differentiation. Your own website with real parent and student testimonials immediately positions you above the noise.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>Capture the win — right after exam results</h3>
      <p>Student just aced the SAT? Parent texts you with the score? That's when you reply: "I'm so proud — would you share a quick testimonial for my website?" Timing is everything.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>Works for online tutors too</h3>
      <p>Fully virtual tutoring businesses need testimonials more than anyone — they don't have local word-of-mouth. Your testimonial widget is always-on social proof for people finding you online.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="steps-section" id="how-it-works">
  <h2>How it works for tutors</h2>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">1</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Get your collection link</h3>
      <p>Sign up free and get a unique link for collecting testimonials. Parents and students click the link, fill out a simple form — no account needed on their end.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">2</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Ask after a win</h3>
      <p>Grade improved? Exam passed? Course completed? Text or email the link: "Your feedback would really help other families find me — would you mind leaving a quick note?" Takes them under 3 minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">3</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Embed on your website</h3>
      <p>Approve what you want displayed. Add the widget to your tutoring website or booking page with one line of code. Works on every website platform.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="own-your-reviews">
  <div class="own-inner">
    <h2>Your reputation is your business</h2>
    <p>As a tutor, your entire business is referral-driven — but most of those referrals happen in conversations you're not part of. A testimonial widget brings those conversations onto your website where they can work 24/7.</p>
    <p>Every parent who finds you through Google, a school directory, or a tutoring platform clicks through to your website to make the final decision. That's where testimonials close the deal.</p>
    <p>Free forever for one active widget. No credit card required.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 8px; display: inline-block;">Try it free</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="quote-section">
  <blockquote>"I'd been teaching for 8 years and had no online presence beyond a basic website. Adding the testimonial widget made my services page feel like a real business. I filled my spring slots 3 weeks earlier than usual."</blockquote>
  <cite>— Math tutor, Austin TX</cite>
</section>

<section class="faq-section">
  <h2>Questions from tutors</h2>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Can parents and students both leave testimonials?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Anyone with the link can submit a testimonial. You can encourage parents to write about academic improvement and students to write about the learning experience — both are valuable for different age groups.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>What if a testimonial mentions a student's name?</h3>
    <p>You review and approve every submission before it's published. If a testimonial includes identifying details you'd prefer to omit, you can request a revision before approving or simply decline that submission.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Does this work for tutoring agencies with multiple tutors?</h3>
    <p>Yes. On the Pro plan you can create multiple widgets — one per tutor, per subject, or per age group — and embed each where most relevant. The free plan gives you one active widget to start.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>What's the free plan?</h3>
    <p>Free forever for one active widget — no credit card, no time limit. Collect unlimited testimonials, display one widget anywhere on your site. Upgrade anytime.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <h2>Turn parent word-of-mouth into a 24/7 sales page</h2>
  <p>Free forever for one widget. Set up in under 5 minutes.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-white">Get started free</a>
</section>

<footer>
  <a href="/">Home</a>
  <a href="/for">All Industries</a>
  <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
  <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
  <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/restaurants" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Restaurants</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
